These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, writer, designer, firefighter
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, garlic, cherry, onion
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, russian, pakistani, japanese
1. the polish is the firefighter##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
3. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
4. the russian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
6. the japanese is on the left of the designer##1
7. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the japanese is between the person eating onion and the dressmaker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Job         | firefighter      | dressmaker | writer | designer |
| Food   | cherry | raspberry  | garlic   | onion    |
| Nationality     | polish     | pakistani    | japanese    | russian      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rugby, skateboarding, ice-hockey
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, september, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, blue, red, coral
1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is rugby##2
8. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | skateboarding   | rugby | handball  |
| Birthday   | september     | july | december  | january |
| Color     | coral        | red  | blue    | turquise |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, ferret, cat
4 different games are played: canasta, poker, snooker, bridge
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, teacher, chef, manager
1. the person playing bridge is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the cat##2
2. the person playing poker is the manager##1
3. the freelancer is the owner of the ferret##1
4. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing snooker is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person playing canasta##2
7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | horse | chinchilla   | cat     | ferret     |
| Game   | poker  | bridge | snooker   | canasta  |
| Job     | manager      | teacher | chef | freelancer |

