.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, tea, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, marigold, balloon-flower
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, woodworking, reading, filmmaking
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person drinking tea is the person who growssunflower##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite  | soy-milk   | tea     | cola |
| Flower   | marigold  | balloon-flower      | sunflower        | amaryllis     |
| Hobby         | reading | writing | filmmaking | woodworking   |

