.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
House: ranch-style, craftsman, cottage, victorian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, old-henry, pall-mall, prince
City: hamburg, colone, miami, liverpool
1. the victorian house is the prince-smoker##1
2. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to hamburg is the prince-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
6. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
7. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
8. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
9. the vegafina-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| House   | ranch-style   | victorian   | cottage | craftsman |
| Cigar         | old-henry      | prince | vegafina      | pall-mall |
| City     | colone | hamburg        | liverpool       | miami  |

