.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, fanta, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, rock, indie, dubstep
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, poker, domino
1. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the person playing whist is the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
8. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | fanta   | tea      | water       | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | dubstep | indie     | rock |
| Game     | domino     | backgammon  | whist | poker |

