.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, quad-bike, car
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, whist, canasta
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian, argentine, french
1. the argentine is the person playing billiard##1
2. the nigerian is between the person playing canasta and the dutch##2
3. the person playing canasta is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the car##1
7. the person playing billiard is the person driving the train##1
8. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Transport      | quad-bike   | car          | taxi | train        |
| Game   | whist     | mah-jongg | canasta   | billiard     |
| Nationality           | dutch | nigerian         | french         | argentine |

