.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
House: craftsman, farmhouse, colonial, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, weightlifting, handball
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, pakistani, japanese, french
1. the french is on the left or right of the japanese##3
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the craftsman house##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is the colonial house##1
4. the colonial house is on the right of the japanese##1
5. the pakistani is between the person who's sport is rugby and the craftsman house##2
6. the french is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
7. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
8. the craftsman house is between the farmhouse house and the colonial house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| House         | farmhouse | craftsman      | colonial       | gothic-revival    |
| Sport           | soccer  | weightlifting  | handball | rugby |
| Nationality   | french      | japanese | pakistani         | brazilian    |

