.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop, classical, salsa
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, fishing, puzzles
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, tram, helicopter, boat
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of soul##1
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the fan of classical##1
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop         | soul  | classical     | salsa         |
| Hobby        | puzzles | magic-tricks | board-games | fishing         |
| Transport      | tram         | helicopter  | subway   | boat |

