.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, wooden, tower
There 4 different types of food: corn, cauliflower, lettuce, pear
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, sports, romance, action
 1. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
 2. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the person eating lettuce is between the ranch-style house and the cape-cod house##2
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 6. the person watching action movies is the wooden house##1
 7. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
 8. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating cauliflower is between the tower house and the wooden house##2
10. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| House   | cape-cod  | wooden    | ranch-style | tower    |
| Food   | corn | lettuce | cauliflower  | pear |
| Movie-Genre           | romance   | action    | epic        | sports   |

