.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, aconite, azalea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, folk, rock, indie
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, chinchilla, fish
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
4. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of folk##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the fan of folk##1
8. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Flower      | balloon-flower                | azalea  | bellflower | aconite   |
| Music-Genre           | indie | folk | jazz   | rock |
| Pet   | rabbit         | goldfish     | fish     | chinchilla |

