.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, baccarat, blend, bluemaster
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, sudoku, gardening
4 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, frog, pony
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the owner of the pony##2
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
7. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar          | blend    | baccarat  | bluemaster  | prince |
| Hobby   | gardening | magic-tricks | writing | sudoku |
| Pet   | frog    | turtle     | pony    | cat |

