.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, drawing, woodworking, board-games
City: liverpool, colone, miami, berlin
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blood-red, grey, azure
1. the person who likes blood-red is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person traveling to liverpool##2
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person who likes azure is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
8. the person traveling to miami is the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes chestnut##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby      | singing | woodworking      | drawing  | board-games    |
| City   | miami   | colone | berlin | liverpool |
| Color           | azure      | grey       | blood-red   | chestnut      |

